g if I was passing them in the hall. I thought that was a nice touch although I do not need to be treated that special, haha. My only regret is not getting to use any of the other amenities as they looked great. They even do turn down service but I did not have them do it for me as I was already in my room for the evening at the times they tried to come. If you don't like this service, just hang your Do Not Disturb sign and they will leave you alone.Besides the stained sheet, a great hotel stay!	
