d the rudest woman we'd ever met when we tried to get into Shark Reef at Mandalay Bay who insisted on seeing photo ID and when we told her that we don't carry photo ID in the UK, she argued with us and became very hostile, refusing our entry, then angrily flashing her hands in a dismissive way and then proceeded to bad mouth us to her colleagues in full view of a waiting queue. We had not raised our voices once and did not feel that her retaliation was either necessary or justified. Sadly we didn't get another opportunity to go back there but found we saw and did plenty anyway.	
