 taxi waiting there - one always needed to be called.This was our first visit to Vegas and I cannot compare this property to others in Vegas - but I would be very surprised if any other property comes close to the Four Seasons in terms of service. For that reason, we would not hesitate in staying here for any return visit, especially if we were travelling with the kids.	
