 experienced this at FS. What I basically found since FS is a HOTEL and not a CASINO, they care more about the service than the casino dollars. With good service they make you want to come back (and that is exactly the way my wife and I feel). Unfortunately, we had too good a time on vacation and its difficult to get back to normal life after being pampered at the FS	
